            </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #E8EAED; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;">Ledger Security Tips</p>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <div class="tip">
